com.github.kskelm.baringo.model

Class Album

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.kskelm.baringo.model.Album

  • public class Album
extends java.lang.Object
    Model object for (non-gallery) albums. GalleryAlbum objects are different in the sense that they contain a subset of information pertinent to listings of items in galleries.
    Author:
    Kevin Kelm (triggur@gmail.com)
